abstract: United Nations Children's Fund says gunmen have kidnapped at least 89 boys in Malakal, South Sudan.
lead_paragraph: An armed group in South Sudan has abducted at least 89 boys in a northern state, the United Nations children’s agency said Saturday.

headline.main: South Sudan: Gunmen Kidnap 89 Boys, Unicef Says
